Bukannya saya pergi mana-mana.

00:47:27.085 --> 00:47:28.085
Adakah anda telah pergi...

00:47:28.655 --> 00:47:29.655
ke temujanji hospital anda?

00:47:30.955 --> 00:47:31.955
